trans-unit.source: Represents the collection of extensibility elements used by the XML Web service.
trans-unit.target: Representerer samling av extensibility-elementer som brukes av XML-webtjenesten.

trans-unit.source: This class cannot be inherited.
trans-unit.target: Denne klassen kan ikke arves.

trans-unit.source: This collection can either contain instances of classes deriving from <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>, or instances of the <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> class.
trans-unit.target: Denne samlingen kan inneholde enten forekomster av klasser som er avledet fra <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>, eller forekomster av <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>klassen.</xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>

trans-unit.source: In a derived class, <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension> class allows users to define extensibility elements in addition to those defined in the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) specification.
trans-unit.target: I en avledet klasse <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>klassen gjør det mulig for brukere å definere extensibility-elementer i tillegg til dem som er definert i Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL)-spesifikasjonen.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtension>

trans-unit.source: Use these in your ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection if you know in advance the type of extensibility element you want to make.
trans-unit.target: Bruk disse i din ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection vet du på forhånd elementtypen extensibility du vil gjøre.

trans-unit.source: Use an <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement> when you do not know the format of an element in advance.
trans-unit.target: Bruk en <xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>Når du ikke vet formatet for et element på forhånd.</xref:System.Xml.XmlElement>

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initialiserer en ny forekomst av den <xref href="System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection"> </xref> klasse.

trans-unit.source: Since many of the classes in the <xref:System.Web.Services.Description> namespace expose an `Extensions` property representing a <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>, the constructor assigns a parent object corresponding to the level within the Web Services Description Language (WSDL) hierarchy where the current `ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection` is nested.
trans-unit.target: Siden mange av klassene i den <xref:System.Web.Services.Description>navneområdet vise en `Extensions` egenskapen som representerer en <xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection>, konstruktøren tilordner et overordnet objekt tilsvarer nivået i hierarkiet Web Services beskrivelse språket (WSDL) der gjeldende `ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection` er nestet.</xref:System.Web.Services.Description.ServiceDescriptionFormatExtensionCollection> </xref:System.Web.Services.Description>

trans-unit.source: For more information about WSDL, see the specification at http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
trans-unit.target: For mer informasjon om WSDL, kan du se spesifikasjonen på http://www.w3.org/TR/wsdl/.
